<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Dear, <%= @user.name %></h1>
    <p>
      You mE2 email account is: <%= @user.email %>.<br/>
    </p>
    <p>
    	The purpose of this letter is to help you to reset your password.<br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      To do that, just follow this link: 
      <%= link_to 'Reset your password now', edit_password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for seeing this letter and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>